powerpc/8xx: Use SPRN_SPRG_SCRATCH2 in DTLB miss exception

Use SPRN_SPRG_SCRATCH2 in DTLB miss exception instead of DAR
in order to be similar to ITLB miss exception.

This also simplifies mpc8xx_pmu_del()

